title: Hanjin Shipping - number of TEUs 2016
summary: This grouped bar chart represents Number of TEUs on the Y-axis. And, its value throughout 8 Months for Owned, Chartered, and Orderbook.
Over the 8 Months, the Number of TEUs for both Owned and Month have reduced.
In Month June 13 2016, Chartered had the highest Number of TEUs 351338.0 among the 3 groups and in July 12 2016, Orderbook had the lowest Number of TEUs 0.0.
In Month August 15 2016, Owned had the maximum Number of TEUs and it saw the lowest in Month July 12 2016 out of all 8 Months.

max_summary: This grouped bar chart represents Number of TEUs on the Y-axis. And, its value throughout 8 Months for Owned, Chartered, and Orderbook.
All through the Months, similar trend was observed for Owned and Month. In both cases, the Number of TEUs have reduced.
Month June 13 2016 had the maximum Number of TEUs among all 3 groups, and it was for Chartered. The minimum Number of TEUs was observed in Month July 12 2016 for Orderbook.
Among all the Months, Owned had the highest Number of TEUs 292311.0 in Month August 15 2016 and lowest value 274078.0 in Month July 12 2016.
The maximum Number of TEUs for Owned that was found in Month August 15 2016 was 1.07 times larger than the minimum Number of TEUs observed in Month July 12 2016.
Among all 3 groups, Chartered had the gap of 33088.0 between the maximum and minimum Number of TEUs observed in Month June 13 2016 and September 7 2016 respectively.

In Month June 13 2016, Chartered had the highest Number of TEUs 351338.0 among the 3 groups and in July 12 2016, Orderbook had the lowest Number of TEUs 0.0. The second highest Number of TEUs 292311.0 was observed for Chartered in Month June 13 2016.
On average, the Month August 15 2016 had the highest Number of TEUs for all 3 groups Owned, Chartered, and Orderbook. Whereas July 12 2016 had the lowest average Number of TEUs.
